about-me.description: Hello! My name is Victor, I'm a Front-End Developer and I love creating things. Since I was a kid I've always had a taste for technology so what motivates me the most is to be part of this amazing world and I'll try to leave my mark on it!

window.description: I love the JavaScript language and it's what I've been using since I started in this programming world, but I'm open to learn any stack whenever there is the opportunity.
